    <briefdescription>
<para>Modernized configuration data structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This type provides a modern YAML-based configuration system with better organization, validation, and extensibility.</para>
<para>Key features:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Better organization with nested types for different categories</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Built-in validation and consistency checking</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Support for dynamic process configuration</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Enhanced debugging and introspection capabilities</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Full YAML configuration support </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
